  "about": {
    "whoWeAreTitle": "Who Are We?",
    "whoWeAreText": "Founded in Kochani in 2002, Oscar d-t is a specialized store offering a carefully curated selection of high-quality bags and accessories. With more than two decades of experience, we are dedicated to providing stylish and accessible pieces that complement each customer's individuality. Our location in Kochani proudly serves the community, delivering a personalized shopping experience focused on quality and modern trends. Discover the perfect accessory for your style at Oscar d-t.",
    "storyTitle": "Our Story",
    "storyParagraph1": "Hello! Welcome to Oscar d-t! We have been part of Kochani's story since 2002 and we truly love helping people find their perfect bag or fashion accessory. Think of us as your favorite place for all those small (and not so small) details that truly complete the look.",
    "storyParagraph2": "For years, we have carefully selected stylish and quality bags and accessories. Whether you are looking for an elegant bag that turns heads or those essential finishing details, you will find the right piece here. It is not only about the products we sell; we genuinely care about making your shopping experience special. We want you to find pieces you absolutely love and that highlight your unique style.",
    "storyParagraph3": "We are right here in Kochani, and through the years we have become a recognizable and friendly face in the neighborhood. We are very proud of the relationships we have built with our community. So come by and explore. We will be happy to help you discover your next favorite bag or the perfect accessory you have been looking for.",
    "signatureQuote": "Elegance is not about being noticed, but about being remembered.",
    "aboutTitle": "About Us",
    "aboutText": "Located in the heart of Kochani since 2002, Oscar d-t Bijouterie is a family business founded by the Rozin-Sopkovi family. We offer a rich collection of high-quality fashion accessories, from refined earrings to stylish bags. With dedication to a diverse and modern selection, we invite you to discover the perfect pieces to express your personal style."
  },
